[normal]Temperature drives both CO2 and water vapor independently
[normal],.
[normal] The whole CA
[normal]GW - GHG scare is based on the obvious fallacy of putting the effect before the cause.
[normal] 
[normal]As a simple (not exact) analogy controlling CO2 levels to control temperature is like trying to lower the temperature of an electric hot plate under a boiling pan of wat
[normal]er by capturing and sequestering the steam coming off the top
[normal] 
[normal].
